title: My Friends Are Doing Better Than I Am
description:
Tyler feels like he's behind in life compared with the friends he grew up with and wonders how he'll ever stop comparing himself to others. - Dr. Laura: "Every person has a unique path to follow."

How do you feel about the path you've chosen in life? Email me your thoughts at: drlaura@drlaura.com
